{"tid":1738482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"選舉管理委員會主席馮驊：事故影響逾1.5小時即押後該區選舉","createTime":"2019-11-19T09:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T16:47:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"32aae43392fda03d3f5355493b73542af5c73239","tid":1738482,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"區議會選舉將於星期日舉行，選舉管理委員會主席馮驊表示，會密切留意情況，如果在選舉當日，個別選區的票站不能進行選舉，該選區便會押後一星期至12月1日再舉行投票。他又強調選舉不會考慮政治因素，如果發生危害公眾安全的事情，便要押後投票，一切視乎當時實際情況，按法律行事。<br />\n<br />\n馮驊說，如果個別票站發生事故，影響時間長過1個半小時，便會決定押後該選區的投票至下月1日再進行。<br />\n<br />\n馮驊說，今次區選比2015年所需的人手多，因為增加了21個選區，而每個選區都有競逐，工作人手很緊張，因此希望不會有事故發生，承傳香港良好的選舉文化，讓413萬名選民投票表達意見。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493254-20191119.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493254-20191119.htm&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=341ea816\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493254-20191119.htm&h=fb39a843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493254-20191119.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6fd5b0028bd80a358122b16c6e428bab9fbd812a","tid":1738482,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"取消la 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個驚d"},{"pid":"584c1f417614af1a80c84493181cf5e08690a2a9","tid":1738482,"uid":193380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:13:25.000Z","msg":"[1119] 五毛新風向：今日冇黎明行動，以後唔再塞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737615</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZyZsqLq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZyZsqLq.png&h=1025d288&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c68c07b85e9ca93e75e29f3715168ba164bcb13f","tid":1738482,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit